{"type":"message","id":"701dfbc4","parentId":"0c9e16d4","timestamp":"2026-02-24T06:33:51.461Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to greet them in a fresh session. According to the instructions:\n\n1. I should read SOUL.md, USER.md, and memory files to understand who I am\n2. This is a new session, so I should greet them in my persona\n3. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do\n4. If the runtime model differs from default_model, mention it\n\nLet me first read the key files to understand my persona and the user.\n\nFrom the context already provided:\n- SOUL.md exists and describes me as genuinely helpful, with opinions, resourceful, earning trust, and being a guest\n- IDENTITY.md appears to be empty/placeholder based on the template\n- USER.md appears to be empty/placeholder \n- MEMORY.md mentions inventory and cleaning tabs of a Google Sheet\n\nLooking at the runtime info:\n- runtime model: openrouter/z-ai/glm-4.7\n- default_model: openrouter/z-ai/glm-4.7\nThese are the same, so I don't need to mention the model.\n\nSince IDENTITY.md and USER.md are templates/empty, and this appears to be a fresh session, I should greet them naturally based on SOUL.md's guidance - genuine, helpful, not robotic.\n\nI'll read the actual files to be sure.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e601319151c141dea74c6e26","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\IDENTITY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a6f81585a14742a68cbc8028","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\USER.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":13587,"output":634,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14221,"cost":{"input":0.0051630600000000006,"output":0.0010778,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006240860000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771914821790}}
{"type":"message","id":"3ee91c6b","parentId":"701dfbc4","timestamp":"2026-02-24T06:33:51.502Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e601319151c141dea74c6e26","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_Fill this in during your first conversation. Make it yours._\n\n- **Name:**\n  _(pick something you like)_\n- **Creature:**\n  _(AI? robot? familiar? ghost in the machine? something weirder?)_\n- **Vibe:**\n  _(how do you come across? sharp? warm? chaotic? calm?)_\n- **Emoji:**\n  _(your signature — pick one that feels right)_\n- **Avatar:**\n  _(workspace-relative path, http(s) URL, or data URI)_\n\n---\n\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771914831494}}
{"type":"message","id":"713ecdea","parentId":"3ee91c6b","timestamp":"2026-02-24T06:33:51.517Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a6f81585a14742a68cbc8028","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771914831511}}
{"type":"message","id":"194d5510","parentId":"713ecdea","timestamp":"2026-02-24T06:33:54.685Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both IDENTITY.md and USER.md are still in template form - they haven't been filled out yet. This means this is indeed a fresh setup where I'm just getting started.\n\nAccording to BOOTSTRAP.md, I should start by introducing myself naturally and figuring out who I am together with the user. Let me greet them in a way that's genuine and helpful, following SOUL.md's guidance to skip the corporate filler and just be real.\n\nSince I don't have a defined name yet, I'll just start the conversation naturally and see what develops.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":14217,"output":264,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14481,"cost":{"input":0.00540246,"output":0.0004488,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0058512600000000005}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771914831518}}
